headline: With $400,000 KeyBank Gift, Hartford Promise Guides Area Students From High School to Career
summary: CLEVELAND, OH / ACCESS Newswire / August 26, 2025 / A $400,000 gift from KeyBank Foundation to Hartford Promise will help support Hartford public school students find success from high school to college to career. Research shows 73% of college graduates ...

headline: KEYCORP TO PRESENT AT THE BARCLAYS GLOBAL FINANCIAL SERVICES CONFERENCE
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) announced today that Randy Paine, Head of Institutional Banking, and Clark Khayat, Chief Financial Officer, will present at the Barclays Global Financial Services Conference on Monday, September 8, 2025, at 12:00 p.m. ET in New York City.
